<P>
   -----
</P>
<P>
   &UR; GOSSIP &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ``ISAAC MIZRAHI SHUTS DOWN.'' From WWD. One B&AMP;W photo. Isaac
Mizrahi dropped a fashion bombshell on Oct. 1: He said his
10-year-old business is closing. Mizrahi, a designer whose
ebullient personality matched his colorful clothing, said his
partnership with Chanel was being dissolved. A report.
</P>
<P>
   -----
</P>
