   &UR; FASHION TRENDS &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   ``TREND WATCH: SPACE CASE.'' From WWD. Three color slides. Bold,
futuristic looks will be landing in stores for spring, as seen in
this fashion pictorial.
</P>
<P>
   ``SPEAKING ENGLISH.'' From WWD. The talk of the town during the
London shows was Alexander McQueen's stellar spring collection.
Here, a review of his work _ and that of his peers.
</P>
<P>
   ``ARRIVA MILANO.'' From WWD. Quick-change artist Miuccia Prada
created clothes-and-accessories combinations for Miu Miu, while
Domenico Dolce and Stefano Gabbana spiked D&AMP;G's clubwear with acid
brights as the spring collections got underway. (slugged:
BC-MILAN-SHOWS-(FASHION)-FAIRCHILD)
</P>
