   WASHINGTON NEWS (``w'' category)
</P>
<P>
   MEDICAL-MARIJUANA (Washington) _ Four Republican senators and
former federal drug policy director William Bennett urge voters not
to approve state ballot initiatives that would follow the 1996
California and Arizona measures legalizing marijuana for medicinal
uses. By JUDY HOLLAND.
</P>
<P>
   COMMENTARY (``k'' category)
</P>
<P>
   GREENSPAN-EUROPE (Paris) _ already filed _ When Federal Reserve
chief Alan Greenspan said this week that in 50 years as a financial
analyst he had never seen anything like the recent turbulence that
has struck financial markets, he sent a wave of cold apprehension
through Europe. By BERNARD D. KAPLAN.
</P>
<P>
