<DOCNO> NYT19981009.0104 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-09 14:08 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A8463 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-SPECTOR-MUSIC-PROFILE     10-09 1147
