compatible interface was what you hoped for on blind dates.''
Echoing the frustration of many a PC user, she wonders, ``Why can't
they write a decent manual, given the thickness of a Russian
novel?'' (slugged:
BC-A-TECHNOPHOBE'S-LAMENT-(HOME-BUSINESS-WEEK)-NYTSF, priority code
