 Friday, Oct. 9, 1998     
 Editors     
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service has filed or will file these stories for
Saturday, Sunday and thereafter. If you have questions, please call
Susie McBee or Tim Spence at 202-298-6920. For questions about
Houston Chronicle sports stories, please call the Houston Chronicle
Sports Department, 713-220-7896.
</P>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   (Adds: CONGRESS-SHUTDOWN; CAPITOL-SHOOTINGS; GLENN-NASA;
BAPTIST-LEADER-PROFILE; NASA-TECH; BBN-ASTROS; INDIAN-GAMING;
FERAL-CATS; MEXICO-POLICIES; MEXICO-GROWTH; and SHELL-TECH.)
