   CONGRESS-REPUBS (Washington) _ While the leaders talk, other
Republicans in the House have put issues on the floor for votes.
These are issues they know will go nowhere, but they are also
issues that they hope to use against Democrats in campaign ads. By
Katharine Q. Seelye.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
