<P>
   FUEL _ Despite a recent uptick, the prices for gasoline, heating
oil and natural gas are at or near all-time lows. But it may not
last for long, and people heating homes with gas may not see a
difference for a while. (Gulliver, Dayton Daily News). 12 WITH
