<P>
   REYNOLDS-REORGANIZATION _ WEST PALM BEACH, Fla. _ A judge
approved Burt Reynolds' plan for reorganization, and the actor will
emerge from bankruptcy protection in the next month. (Kleinberg,
Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   WHOLE-FOODS _ AUSTIN, Texas _ Peter Roy, who has been
instrumental in building Whole Foods Market Inc. into the nation's
largest chain of natural foods supermarkets, has resigned as
president of the Austin-based company. (Breyer, Austin
American-Statesman) MOVED.
</P>
