Online who hosts a weekly chat attended by hundreds, has proven a
huge hit in the year since her oh-so-modest debut. This 25-year-old
Encino native is a true TV junkie who really does follow the ins
and outs of Bailey and Claudia on ``Party of Five,'' Amanda and
Billy on ``Melrose Place.'' 
