CONSERVANCY-CELEBRATION (Los Angeles) _ The Los Angeles
Conservancy, the nation's largest historic preservation group, will
celebrate its 20th anniversary Sunday with guided tours of the
Memorial Coliseum in Exposition Park, kids' kite decorating and
kite flying, food tasting from historic Los Angeles restaurants,
music, a silent auction of specially designed anniversary banners
and a giant birthday cake in the shape of the Coliseum. By Carol
Bidwell. 
. 
CONSERVANCY-TOURS (Los Angeles) _ If you've never gotten out of
your car and taken a moment to look beyond the grit and gridlock in
downtown L.A., here's your chance. The L.A. Conservancy currently
runs 10 tours featuring architectural themes and neighborhoods in
the city. By Caol Bidwell. 
. 
