friends wait and worry, three men remain missing after failing to
return Oct. 2 from a holiday in Orlando, Fla. By William F.
Doherty. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   BELARUS-CHILD (Boston) -- Alexei Anatolevich Saponchikov, a
victim of Chernobyl, has returned to the United States for more
medical treatment. Now a Massachusetts family is fighting to make
the Belarus youngster a full-fledged American. By Gloria Negri.
1100 words.
</P>
<P>
