economy, the number of homeless people in Massachusetts has reached
a record high. By Zachary R. Dowdy. 800 words.
</P>
<P>
   MA-AIDS-DEATHS (Boston) -- AIDS deaths in 1997 in Massachusetts
fell 60 percent, an even greater decline than the year before. By
Richard A. Knox. 700 words.
</P>
