<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-09 20:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9332 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CYC-MOUNTAIN-BOS &LR;      10-09 1097
