   BC-CITIGROUP-OUTLOOK-NYT (moved on Thursday, Oct. 8)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Thursday, Oct. 8,
about Citigroup's third-quarter results misstated the two chief
executives' plans for their work force. While they still plan to
eliminate several thousand jobs, as was announced on Sept. 17, they
said yesterday that they planned no further job cuts beyond that.
</P>
