   An article in Circuits on Thursday about black-oriented Web
sites omitted the caption for a picture showing a sculpture of a
woman with her left hand on her chin. The sculpture was ``Phillis
Wheatley'' by Elizabeth Catlett, from the Neuberger Museum of Art. &QL;
